{"0":"✅ **自動備份設置完成！**\n\n---\n\n## 📋 備份配置\n\n| 項目 | 設定 |\n|------|------|\n| **備份時間** | 每日 00:00 同 18:00 |\n| **備份目標** | `superronclaw/superron-memory` |\n| **備份內容** | Workspace、Skills、Extensions、Logs、Memory |\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 首次備份成功\n\n```\n🔄 Superron 自動備份 - 2026-03-13 20:06:16\n32 files changed, 2630 insertions(+), 337 deletions(-)\n✅ 備份成功！已推送至 GitHub\n```\n\n**已備份項目：**\n- ✅ AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md, USER.md\n- ✅ TOOLS.md, MEMORY.md 等核心記憶\n- ✅ Skills（daily-report, md-to-pdf）\n- ✅ Extensions（kimi-claw, kimi-search, dingtalk）\n- ✅ 配置檔案（openclaw.json）\n- ✅ 系統日志\n\n---\n\n## 🛡️ 保護機制\n\n**如果系統崩潰：**\n1. 記憶檔案已自動上傳 GitHub\n2. 重新部署時 clone 倉庫即可還原\n3. 每日兩次備份，最大損失 12 小時\n\n**備份日志：** `/root/.openclaw/logs/backup.log`\n\n---\n\n下次自動備份：**明日 00:00**\n\n你嘅記憶現在有雙重保護。","_meta":{"runtime":"node","runtimeVersion":"22.22.0","hostname":"unknown","name":"openclaw","date":"2026-03-13T12:06:31.367Z","logLevelId":3,"logLevelName":"INFO","path":{"fullFilePath":"file:///usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CiM1FVu6.js:272:46","fileName":"subsystem-CiM1FVu6.js","fileNameWithLine":"subsystem-CiM1FVu6.js:272","fileColumn":"46","fileLine":"272","filePath":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CiM1FVu6.js","filePathWithLine":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CiM1FVu6.js:272","method":"console.log"}},"time":"2026-03-13T12:06:31.367Z"}
