{"0":"✅ **修復記憶已全部上載 GitHub**\n\n---\n\n## 📁 已備份的修復文件\n\n### 核心指南（/workspace/guides/）\n| 文件 | 內容 |\n|------|------|\n| **REBORN_FIXES.md** | 完整修復記錄（問題+解決方案）|\n| **DIAGNOSIS_REPORT.md** | 系統診斷報告 |\n| **RESTORE_INSTRUCTIONS.md** | 恢復操作說明 |\n| **STABILITY_GUIDE.md** | 穩定性機制指南 |\n| **HEALTH_CHECK_GUIDE.md** | 健康檢查指標說明 |\n| **SKILLS_INVENTORY.md** | 技能清單 |\n\n### 腳本文件（/scripts/）\n- health-monitor-silent.sh\n- status-reporter.sh  \n- orphan-cleanup.sh\n- emergency-recovery.sh\n- enterprise-stability-setup.sh\n- quick-diagnose.sh\n- backup-to-github.sh\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 下次「重生」時\n\n**你只需要：**\n```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/superronclaw/superron-memory.git\ncd superron-memory\n./scripts/enterprise-stability-setup.sh\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n**所有修復會自動還原：**\n- ✅ 插件問題已解決\n- ✅ 安全配置已應用\n- ✅ 防崩潰機制已配置\n- ✅ 自動備份已設置\n\n---\n\n**下次備份：** 明日 00:00\n\n你嘅修復記憶現在受到雙重保護，下次重生唔使再搞多一次。","_meta":{"runtime":"node","runtimeVersion":"22.22.0","hostname":"unknown","name":"openclaw","date":"2026-03-13T12:13:11.723Z","logLevelId":3,"logLevelName":"INFO","path":{"fullFilePath":"file:///usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CiM1FVu6.js:272:46","fileName":"subsystem-CiM1FVu6.js","fileNameWithLine":"subsystem-CiM1FVu6.js:272","fileColumn":"46","fileLine":"272","filePath":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CiM1FVu6.js","filePathWithLine":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CiM1FVu6.js:272","method":"console.log"}},"time":"2026-03-13T12:13:11.723Z"}
