{"0":"**已準備好配置流程。**\n\n---\n\n## 📱 Telegram 配置步驟\n\n### 你需要做（1分鐘）：\n1. 打開 Telegram，搜尋 **@BotFather**\n2. 撳 `/newbot`\n3. 輸入名稱（如：Superron）\n4. 輸入用戶名（如：superron_bot，必須以 **bot** 結尾）\n5. **複製 BotFather 俾你嘅 Token**\n   - 格式：`123456789:ABCdefGHIjklMNOpqrsTUVwxyz`\n\n### 我會做（攞到 Token 後）：\n- ✅ 更新 `openclaw.json` 配置\n- ✅ 重啟 Gateway\n- ✅ 測試連接\n\n---\n\n**請而家去 Telegram 攞 Token，攞到之後貼俾我。**\n\n（或者如果你已經有 Bot Token，直接貼俾我）","_meta":{"runtime":"node","runtimeVersion":"22.22.0","hostname":"unknown","name":"openclaw","date":"2026-03-13T12:15:54.155Z","logLevelId":3,"logLevelName":"INFO","path":{"fullFilePath":"file:///usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CiM1FVu6.js:272:46","fileName":"subsystem-CiM1FVu6.js","fileNameWithLine":"subsystem-CiM1FVu6.js:272","fileColumn":"46","fileLine":"272","filePath":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CiM1FVu6.js","filePathWithLine":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-CiM1FVu6.js:272","method":"console.log"}},"time":"2026-03-13T12:15:54.156Z"}
